dia/9c36af533bd9ace7757e6a32b6249349c57ab874/327_138_846_846/master/846.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/9c36af533bd9ace7757e6a32b6249349c57ab874/327_138_846_846/master/846.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/9c36af533bd9ace7757e6a32b6249349c57ab874/327_138_846_846/master/846.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/9c36af533bd9ace7757e6a32b6249349c57ab874/327_138_846_846/master/846.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 320px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/9c36af533bd9ace7757e6a32b6249349c57ab874/327_138_846_846/master/846.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Grey pleated tartan skirt\" src=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/9c36af533bd9ace7757e6a32b6249349c57ab874/327_138_846_846/master/846.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" width=\"445\" height=\"445\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe vortex of disappointment which hit me after failing to snag one of the pleated short skirts from the Bella Freud x M\u0026amp;S collection made me realise how much I want – need – the kind of pleated above-the-knee skirt I haven’t worn since school uniform days. I went down an eBay rabbit hole, and can report that this is an excellent source of the new skirt shape you need. I’m still deciding between \u003ca href