 leather belt\" src=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/9d910599845b3e2d3e7f00e5031c17b03cbd4cdf/320_450_3126_1876/master/3126.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" width=\"445\" height=\"267.05694177863086\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg width=\"18\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 13\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M18 3.5v8l-1.5 1.5h-15l-1.5-1.5v-8l1.5-1.5h3.5l2-2h4l2 2h3.5l1.5 1.5zm-9 7.5c1.9 0 3.5-1.6 3.5-3.5s-1.6-3.5-3.5-3.5-3.5 1.6-3.5 3.5 1.6 3.5 3.5 3.5z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e Photograph: Sarah Lee/The Guardian\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eDo you own a belt? Any belt? Then you have a new outfit. This is what you do. Wear the longest sweater you own – one that covers your bum – over wide trousers, or a really long skirt. Then cinch your waist with a belt. And add heels. \u003cem\u003eSo \u003c/em\u003echic.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"a-hair-claw-to-make-you-smile\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA hair claw to make you smile\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"fec1b594-6f57-4f98-bc1d-3aa1f38306d9\" data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.ImageBlockElement\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"img-12\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/1e06e6dc4eef4db3b1d2d9a5d560b151fc02c369/468_541_976_976/master/976.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 660px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/1e06e6dc4eef4db3b1d2d9a5d560b151fc02c369/468_541_976_976/master/976.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/1e06e6dc4eef4db3b1d2d9a5d560b151f